Build at the IDC:
-----------------

  autoreconf --verbose --force --install
  ./configure --prefix=/where/to/install/cbase \
              --enable-idc \
              --with-pic
  make
  make check
  make install

  Configure for RHEL 5 systems:
  -----------------------------

    ./configure --prefix=/where/to/install/cbase \
                --with-pic

Build outside the IDC:
----------------------

  autoreconf --verbose --force --install
  ./configure --prefix=/where/to/install/cbase \
              --with-pic
  make
  make check
  make install

